  "keyFeatures": [
    "Cross-platform process and memory manipulation (Windows/Linux/FreeBSD)",
    "Internal and external memory operations",
    "Function hooking and detouring with trampoline support",
    "Memory pattern and signature scanning",
    "JIT assembly and disassembly via Keystone and Capstone",
    "VMT (Virtual Method Table) hooking",
    "Module enumeration and dynamic loading/injection",
    "Multi-architecture support (x86, x64, ARM, ARM64)",
    "Bindings for C, Modern C++, Rust, and Python"
